    "is_free": false,
    "description": "Embark on a side-splitting adventure in SideQuest: Reanimated, a side-scrolling action RPG set in the enchanting world of Mederlund. Follow the uproarious escapades of a delightfully unconventional band of heroes. You'll enjoy strategic combat, a wealth of unique quests, and deeply customizable character builds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TAKE ON CHALLENGING (AND FUNNY!) QUESTS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/2ea3bb2c1654caa86b71bed8982d7f46.poster.avif?t=1721601785\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/2ea3bb2c1654caa86b71bed8982d7f46.webm?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/2ea3bb2c1654caa86b71bed8982d7f46.mp4?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As the name suggests, there’s no shortage of quests in Sidequest! Discover hilarious NPCs, defeat cool bosses and navigate a huge number of quests - many of them with unique challenges and minigames for you to conquer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE FROM 5 PLAYABLE CHARACTERS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/fc21df44ea613d7814e695bbe8fb8e5e.poster.avif?t=1721601785\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/fc21df44ea613d7814e695bbe8fb8e5e.webm?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/fc21df44ea613d7814e695bbe8fb8e5e.mp4?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose from 5 playable characters - each one with unique abilities, looks and personality! Each character has 2 talent builds to choose from - so whether looking to be a damage dealer, tank or support, there’s a character for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DEEP CUSTOMIZATION AND ONE-OF-A-KIND BUILDS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/a87ebfc9350cd4e1db2e88a5ca5c7e31.poster.avif?t=1721601785\" width=600 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/a87ebfc9350cd4e1db2e88a5ca5c7e31.webm?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/a87ebfc9350cd4e1db2e88a5ca5c7e31.mp4?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Feeling creative? Craft your own path to victory with hugely customizable characters - choosing their abilities, stats and gear to come up with unique synergies and builds! Choose your own playstyle - and create builds that nobody has ever seen before!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EMBARK SOLO OR WITH FRIENDS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/9fc06e95e1501aa3ff4cb80d35163528.poster.avif?t=1721601785\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/9fc06e95e1501aa3ff4cb80d35163528.webm?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/9fc06e95e1501aa3ff4cb80d35163528.mp4?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You’re never alone in Sidequest - whether you embark solo with your NPC companions joining you, or whether you play multiplayer co-op with your friends, you’ll always have a party by your side!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30+ quests planned for release!<br></li><li>Choose from 5 playable characters, each one with 2 talent builds!<br></li><li>20+ different enemy types.<br></li><li>A deep progression system of loot, upgrades and skills!<br></li><li>Multiplayer and single-player capabilities.<br></li><li>Unique, funny dialogue and NPCs to discover!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/39bc22720917a80ac2e17e39a9e0f511.poster.avif?t=1721601785\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/39bc22720917a80ac2e17e39a9e0f511.webm?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/39bc22720917a80ac2e17e39a9e0f511.mp4?t=1721601785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
